title: Hannah Einbinder | FDA Warns People Not to Use Horse De-Wormer Ivermectin to Treat COVID: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at the FDA warning people not to take livestock de-wormer as GOP politicians continue to oppose mask and vaccine mandates.

Hannah Einbinder talks about her role in Hacks, having her chops busted by Jean Smart and supporting herself at the start of her stand-up career.
